name: TENEBRIS.WAD
description: Nazis are back! Your Headquarter informs you that the good old Adolf H. is reincarnated in an Archvile. In the bowels of the earth, he is recruiting Zombies & Demons, in order to appease his thirst for power. But it is not enough... He want to see the swastika waving on the Tower of London. And this time he's furiously angry...
